caption:
“I’m happy to be alive.”

Jessica Driffill is one of two moms to ever give birth in the Cath Lab at Strong Memorial—this was because her heart needed close monitoring throughout labor & delivery.

Now, seven years later, she’s still here with her son because of LVAD, a life-saving mobile heart pump that helps her feel better and live her life. ❤️ #advanceshappenhere
